Nelson Mandela Bay municipality staff are attempting  to restore  power supply to areas affected by a “lost supply” on Wednesday. Municipal spokesperson, Mthubanzi Mniki, failed to elaborate as to the reason behind the disruption. "[There is ] a lost supply from Chelsea and Rowallan Park substations affecting Greenbushes, Chelsea, Rowallan Park, Walmer, Arlington, South End, Lorraine, Driftsands / Lovemore Park (DLP), Summerstrand, Seaview (SEA), Theescombe / Chelsea (THC) and surrounding areas.” “Staff attending to restoration of supply, no time frame available,” Mniki said.